{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "丁鹏是一个二十岁的年轻剑客，以一招\"天外流星\"连续击败了史定、葛奇、郭正平三位名剑客。今天他要挑战名满天下的\"青松剑客\"柳若松，以求出人头地。丁鹏出身贫寒，父亲是无名镖师，临终留下残缺剑谱\"天外流星\"。决战当日，丁鹏在万松山庄附近用餐时，一个赤裸的美丽女孩闯入，求他帮助。丁鹏脱衣相赠、分享食物，女孩自称被恶人绑架后逃出，请丁鹏去找她七十岁穿红衣的长辈。丁鹏前往溪水尽头，却落入陷阱被吊在树上，树下两位老人专心下棋不理他，红衣小猴子还向他投掷脏物，令他几近崩溃。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng_zhi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏之父",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "你一定要练成这一剑，一定替我争口气，让别人知道我丁某人也有个出人头地的儿子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "救救我，你一定要救救我。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "你……你……你能不能把衣服脱下来借给我。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "谢谢！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "是不是有人在追你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "这地方很偏僻，别人很难找得到，就算有人追来，你也不必怕。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "有我这个人和这把刀在，你就不必怕。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "谢谢。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你为什么要逃，是谁在追你？为什么追你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "这些东西全是干净的，你吃一点。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "谢谢！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "不客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "这些给你吃。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "能够遇见你，算是我的运气。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "那些人在哪里，我跟你去找他们！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "你不能去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "有些事，现在我还不能说出来，可是以后我一定会告诉你。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "现在我去找到一个人，就可以安心了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "你要找什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "是我的一位长辈，已经有七十岁了，却还是穿大红的衣服，你要是遇见他，就一定能认得出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "你能不能替我去找他？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "listener_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "text": "不知道这位老先生在什么地方？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "你肯帮我去找他？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "你真是个好人，我永远忘不了你的！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "你沿着溪水往上走，走到水源尽头，就看得见一棵形状很奇特的古树，天气好的时候，他定会在那里下棋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "你看见他之后，一定要先把他正在下的那盘棋搞乱，他才会听你说话，才会跟你来！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_luo_nv_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赤裸女孩",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "listener_name": "丁鹏",
      "text": "我在这里等候，不管你找不找得到他，都一定要快点回来。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chuan_hong_yi_lao_ren",
      "listener_name": "红衣老人",
      "text": "两位老先生，请劳驾把我放下来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_chuan_hong_yi_lao_ren",
      "listener_name": "红衣老人",
      "text": "喂……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    }
